character.name: I. OVERALL SILHOUETTE  His body is tall, upright, and unnervingly still. The clothing is layered, forming a narrow but powerful silhouette. Despite the relatively slim build, he exudes quiet intensity, enhanced by the long trailing shapes around his arms and back that flicker like torn shadows.  II. HOOD & HEAD DESIGN  The most defining feature is the large, heavy hood pulled deep over his head. It forms a sharp, downward-angled shape, almost like the beak of a raven. The folds of the hood are massive and structured, giving him an imposing, monastic severity.  Beneath the hood is a pitch-black helmet or mask, smooth and reflective with an inhuman coldness.  The visor is sleek and featureless, shaped like a narrow vertical wedge.  A jagged, red crack runs across the right side of the mask, glowing like a wound leaking digital light.  Occasional sparks of red flicker at the edges, suggesting instability or power beneath the surface.  This mix of emptiness and minimal detail gives his face a chilling, unreadable presence.  III. CLOAK & UPPER GARMENTS  The cloak draped around him is deep purple, almost black, with heavy shading that adds depth and weight.  Its edges are uneven, dissolving into chaotic pixel fragments as if the fabric is decaying, glitching, or evaporating.  Faint red veins run across the fabric, highlighting its folds and giving it a subtle glow.  Beneath the cloak, a structured chestplate or cloth armor is visible. It is made of overlapping angular panels, also in shades of purple and dark red. A central red ornament—possibly a gemstone, seal, or energy core—sits at the base of the neck, drawing attention to the center of the figure.  IV. ARMS & HANDS  His arms are wrapped in dark garments that appear both rigid and organic.  The right side in particular shows streams of jagged red energy fragments, trailing downward like strips of corrupted cloth.  These distortions give the impression that parts of his arm are dissolving or transforming into raw energy.  His hands are obscured in darkness or gloves, maintaining the mysterious, untouchable nature of the character.  V. LOWER BODY & LEGS  The lower half is practical and minimal, contrasting the dramatic upper design.  Dark leggings or fitted trousers define a lithe, agile physique.  Boots are simple but sturdy, adding solid grounding to his otherwise unstable form.  There is no unnecessary decoration—every line is functional, keeping attention on the upper body and mask.  VI. AURA & SPECIAL VISUAL EFFECTS  Surrounding the character is a subtle but persistent corruption aura:  Black and dark-red particles rise and fall around him like drifting ash.  Some areas distort as if affected by noise or glitch artifacts, enhancing his supernatural aura.  The right side flickers with stronger red distortion, marking it as a source of unstable energy.  This aura makes him feel like a being existing between physical form and digital decay.
